# The inventory management software crashes intermittently so, we need to do the following steps:
We need to scan the pc for corrupt system files.
Booting your pc to clean boot mode.
Use system built in antivirus and run scan for malware.
For more information please check this website. 
https://www.guidingtech.com/top-ways-to-fix-app-crashes-on-windows-10/

remove the last windows update by uninstalling the last update.
Temporarily disable your antivirus.
Search for updating your software.
Reinstall the software or troubleshoot the action that is causing it.
For more information please check this website.
https://windowsreport.com/apps-crash-creators-update/

